I regret not treating Zefang well

285
00:16:40,830 --> 00:16:43,090
and not telling Zefang my true thoughts.

286
00:16:44,330 --> 00:16:45,500
Would he think

287
00:16:46,070 --> 00:16:47,230
I was with him

288
00:16:47,230 --> 00:16:48,760
only because of Ye Haiyuan?

289
00:16:49,100 --> 00:16:50,370
If I die,

290
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,500
does it mean I can meet Zefang?

291
00:16:52,570 --> 00:16:53,310
Don't jinx it!

292
00:16:53,310 --> 00:16:55,910
Young people
shouldn't talk about "death" so lightly.

293
00:16:55,910 --> 00:16:57,320
If Zefang were here,

294
00:16:57,470 --> 00:16:59,530
he wouldn't want to see you like this.

295
00:17:04,410 --> 00:17:05,510
Wait for me.

296
00:17:05,530 --> 00:17:06,190
Wait for me.

297
00:17:06,190 --> 00:17:06,990
Just a moment.

298
00:17:22,460 --> 00:17:25,460
This is Zefang's footprint
recorded after his birth.

299
00:17:25,859 --> 00:17:26,770
As I recall,

300
00:17:27,030 --> 00:17:28,630
he weighed only 2,400 grams.

301
00:17:35,100 --> 00:17:36,970
This is a photo of him
taken on his one-month birthday.

302
00:17:36,970 --> 00:17:38,120
Isn't he adorable?

303
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:40,830
Let me tell you.

304
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:42,230
He was really hard to take care of.

305
00:17:42,230 --> 00:17:43,820
He cried nonstop every night

306
00:17:43,820 --> 00:17:45,820
and didn't even like drinking milk.

307
00:18:01,540 --> 00:18:02,340
What is this?

308
00:18:04,700 --> 00:18:05,500
Well, this...

309
00:18:06,280 --> 00:18:09,020
I made this for his grandma.

310
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:11,400
Before she passed away,

311
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:13,340
she told me to keep this with me

312
00:18:13,620 --> 00:18:15,480
and said she would come back to me.

313
00:18:17,930 --> 00:18:20,190
Don't they say people have an obsession?

314
00:18:21,660 --> 00:18:23,230
Sometimes I think,

315
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:27,020
that might be the reason
why I've been brought back to life,

316
00:18:27,660 --> 00:18:30,920
so that there's a chance to meet her again
in this lifetime.

317
00:18:32,410 --> 00:18:34,630
If she were to reincarnate immediately
after death,

318
00:18:34,630 --> 00:18:36,360
she would be the same age as you.

319
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:39,380
So,

320
00:18:40,050 --> 00:18:40,950
we don't know

321
00:18:40,950 --> 00:18:42,380
what will happen next.

322
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:43,920
But I believe,

323
00:18:45,260 --> 00:18:46,660
if Zefang comes back,

324
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:49,040
you can do better.

325
00:19:00,730 --> 00:19:02,400
I really miss Zefang.

326
00:19:39,670 --> 00:19:40,840
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

327
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:42,410
Go away!

328
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:00,760
Cha!

329
00:20:37,430 --> 00:20:38,330
Ye Haiyuan.

330
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,930
Can you stop being so childish?

331
00:20:43,650 --> 00:20:45,180
If you don't understand me,

332
00:20:46,770 --> 00:20:48,370
at least learn to respect me.

333
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:50,230
I don't respect you?

334
00:20:50,740 --> 00:20:51,510
So,

335
00:20:51,840 --> 00:20:53,350
I should've sent you there myself

336
00:20:53,350 --> 00:20:54,880
and closed the door for you?

337
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:58,270
I just felt sorry for him.

338
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:03,560
Could you

339
00:21:03,560 --> 00:21:05,620
stop being so overly compassionate?

340
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:10,240
Because he didn't believe
I wasn't Xia Zefang.

341
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:13,130
So now he believes,

342
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:15,040
and you hugged him.

343
00:21:15,230 --> 00:21:16,930
I didn't.

344
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:19,030
He's injured.

345
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:21,070
How could I ignore him?

346
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:24,210
Besides,
the red thread is connected to him now.

347
00:21:24,210 --> 00:21:25,830
It means he might be Yu Chan.

348
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:28,260
How can I ignore him?

349
00:21:28,580 --> 00:21:29,830
If he's Yu Chan,

350
00:21:30,820 --> 00:21:31,760
what about me?

351
00:21:32,890 --> 00:21:34,690
When you die, you die. That's it.

352
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:36,350
There is no reincarnation.

353
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:38,920
You've been living in your world.

354
00:21:38,970 --> 00:21:40,260
Why don't you look forward?

355
00:21:40,260 --> 00:21:41,530
What do you know?

356
00:21:48,710 --> 00:21:50,250
What I have in this life

357
00:21:52,230 --> 00:21:53,160
is this limited.

358
00:21:53,870 --> 00:21:55,860
Everything I have has been put in.

359
00:21:57,410 --> 00:21:59,740
I want to follow them
and leave this world.

360
00:22:01,350 --> 00:22:03,480
Do you think it's good to be left alone?

361
00:22:09,680 --> 00:22:11,180
When I miss someone,

362
00:22:12,290 --> 00:22:14,260
I can only hold this iron box,

363
00:22:15,770 --> 00:22:17,310
with no one to talk to.

364
00:22:20,130 --> 00:22:20,840
Yes.

365
00:22:22,150 --> 00:22:24,610
I didn't do enough good deeds
in my past life.

366
00:22:25,410 --> 00:22:28,470
So I can only think about the past
all alone in this life.

367
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:31,280
I'm sorry.

368
00:22:31,610 --> 00:22:33,740
Cha, I didn't know about these things.

369
00:22:38,540 --> 00:22:39,500
Ye Haiyuan.

370
00:22:41,910 --> 00:22:44,780
Do you know
what this iron box means to me?

371
00:22:50,790 --> 00:22:52,050
You don't understand.

372
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:56,320
These are all promises I failed to keep.

373
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:59,560
Young Master died for me.

374
00:23:00,830 --> 00:23:02,230
Yu Chan waited for me.

375
00:23:07,210 --> 00:23:08,470
It doesn't matter now.

376
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:11,710
Now that the box is broken like this,

377
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:14,850
it's time to wake up.

378
00:23:30,430 --> 00:23:31,500
Leave me alone.

379
00:23:43,180 --> 00:23:44,020
Cha!

380
00:24:45,180 --> 00:24:45,980
Zefang.

381
00:24:49,340 --> 00:24:50,180
Zefang.

382
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:53,460
Why are you staying in my body?

383
00:24:53,950 --> 00:24:55,360
Am I not supposed to live?

384
00:24:56,090 --> 00:24:57,730
What are you talking about?

385
00:24:58,810 --> 00:25:00,110
Give me back my body.

386
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:02,960
It was yours to begin with.

387
00:25:04,330 --> 00:25:05,790
Aren't you reluctant?

388
00:25:06,770 --> 00:25:08,970
Everyone likes you and doesn't like me.

389
00:25:13,540 --> 00:25:14,670
I'm wondering

390
00:25:17,540 --> 00:25:19,010
if this trip

391
00:25:20,610 --> 00:25:23,010
can really help me understand my grandson,

392
00:25:24,910 --> 00:25:26,910
so that I won't have so many regrets.

393
00:25:40,470 --> 00:25:41,470
Zefang,

394
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:44,280
don't be unhappy.

395
00:25:45,870 --> 00:25:47,670
The more people feel miserable,

396
00:25:49,260 --> 00:25:50,720
the more unhappy they are.

397
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:54,260
You have to confirm

398
00:25:56,180 --> 00:25:58,060
that you can come back

399
00:25:59,380 --> 00:26:00,910
after I give back your body.

400
00:26:05,630 --> 00:26:06,490
Grandpa.

401
00:26:11,290 --> 00:26:14,090
I haven't heard you call me Grandpa
for a long time.

402
00:26:17,390 --> 00:26:18,560
I still remember

403
00:26:19,220 --> 00:26:21,280
the first time you called me Grandpa.

404
00:26:24,130 --> 00:26:25,660
After you moved here later,

405
00:26:26,090 --> 00:26:27,460
you pulled me and told me

406
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:29,210
you didn't want to go to school.

407
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:30,720
I hit your butt.

408
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:32,770
You cried.

409
00:26:34,220 --> 00:26:35,380
I cried too.

410
00:26:39,790 --> 00:26:41,030
Later,

411
00:26:41,650 --> 00:26:43,250
you went to school in Taipei.

412
00:26:45,530 --> 00:26:47,110
I seldom saw you.

413
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:50,970
I'm sorry, Grandpa.

414
00:26:51,500 --> 00:26:53,100
I didn't spend time with you.

415
00:26:53,340 --> 00:26:54,870
I forgot to accompany you.

416
00:26:55,410 --> 00:26:57,270
I didn't want you to accompany me.

417
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:00,410
I was just afraid

418
00:27:02,370 --> 00:27:03,970
I didn't know what you needed

419
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:05,550
and what you wanted.

420
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:08,340
I didn't take good care of you.

421
00:27:10,450 --> 00:27:12,150
But I have to thank you.

422
00:27:13,760 --> 00:27:15,060
I've had a lot of fun

423
00:27:15,650 --> 00:27:17,810
for the past six months.

424
00:27:19,350 --> 00:27:20,520
I even

425
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:21,770
dated Haiyuan

426
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:24,600
by staying in your body.

427
00:27:26,170 --> 00:27:27,560
I have no regrets now.

428
00:27:30,070 --> 00:27:31,920
Things you think don't matter

429
00:27:33,750 --> 00:27:36,460
are just what I never tried to do.

430
00:27:41,080 --> 00:27:42,350
Remember,

431
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:45,370
even if it's just a few days,

432
00:27:47,030 --> 00:27:48,520
as long as you live life to the fullest,

433
00:27:48,520 --> 00:27:49,550
it's worth it.

434
00:27:51,800 --> 00:27:53,060
You should cherish it.

435
00:27:55,140 --> 00:27:56,540
Don't complain anymore.

436
00:27:58,370 --> 00:27:59,270
Be good.

437
00:28:06,370 --> 00:28:07,140
Grandpa!

438
00:28:20,260 --> 00:28:24,260
[If you want it,
I'll give it back to you.]
